General Information
===================

Installation
============

In order to build helloworld you will need to have some development 
tools installed on your machine. This is the list of packages that 
you can get through apt (if using Debian based distro).

build-essential

=== Running Autotools ===

First untar the package onto your local file system. Then from the 
command line execute the normal Autotools commands from the directory 
that you unpacked codeslayer.

cd ~/codeslayer-x.x
compile
make
sudo make install
